# Modular architecture

See [`docs/agent-playbook/modular-architecture.md`](../../docs/agent-playbook/modular-architecture.md) and skill `edunudg-modular-features`.

- **Theme:** `@edunudg/ui` primitives for all app screens.
- **Features:** one folder per capability under `apps/web/src/features/`.
- **Services:** `apps/web/src/services/` for auth, payments, integrations, shared DB helpers.
- **Flags:** gate nav, routes, and sensitive RPCs — default new integrations OFF.
